data.description: This 3 bedroom home looks over the city of Logan in the heart of downtown. This home offers ample space, upper and lower balconies, and a full walk out basement. Living here you would be close to food, shopping, Central Elementary School and the Logan Aquatic Center. Enjoy the benefit of living in town with Hocking Hills State Park only 20 minutes away! This home would be great for investors, or even a first home!
